.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, biathlon, swimming, soccer
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: sailingmaster, october, december, september, june
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the british is the person who's sport is biathlon
2. the swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming
5. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking coffee
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the bird
7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in october
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october
12. the person who's birthday is in sailingmaster is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the person who's birthday is in september
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing
15. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
